Marti took her SATs

05:51.167 --> 05:53.000
'and what happened
at her high school graduation'

05:53.000 --> 05:54.125
and her 21st birthday--

05:54.125 --> 05:55.458
Okay, in 20 minutes

05:55.458 --> 05:57.208
