out in front of a crowd.

05:57.208 --> 05:59.500
- What can I do to help her?
- Get rid of mom.

05:59.500 --> 06:02.209
'Marti's one of the most
capable people I've ever met.'

06:02.209 --> 06:05.125
You help get her head cleared,
she'll come through.

06:05.125 --> 06:08.166
Positive attitude.
I like the way you think.

06:08.166 --> 06:10.042
Good talk.

06:15.417 --> 06:18.000
I just don't understand,
Marti, why I can't stay.

06:18.000 --> 06:20.333
