right now, please.

06:21.208 --> 06:24.375
I love you
and I am so proud of you

06:24.375 --> 06:26.166
and, Marti, Marti

06:26.166 --> 06:29.083
I wouldn't miss
one of your events for
the whole wide world.

06:29.083 --> 06:32.208
Look at that eyeliner,
you look like
a truck stop tranny.

06:32.208 --> 06:33.417
Mom!

06:33.417 --> 06:35.750
This is the first time
I've competed in anything

06:35.750 --> 06:36.875
since I quit gymnastics

06:36.875 --> 06:39.042
and my entire future
is on the line.

06:39.042 --> 06:41.084
Look, I, I can't focus on me

06:41.084 --> 06:43.084
when I have to deal
with things like being paged

06:43.084 --> 06:44.792
