to manage me.

06:48.125 --> 06:50.041
She loves you,
but you have to go.

06:51.583 --> 06:53.500
My name is Savannah Monroe,
by the way.

06:53.500 --> 06:56.209
Truly a pleasure to meet you.
Let's walk this way.

06:56.834 --> 07:00.125
